PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779199898
OL,3,CTwo 24-hour strikes planned by London
OL,4,CUnderground drivers are called off
OL,6,F"The dispute is not over and more
OL,7,Fstrike action will follow if we fail
OL,8,Fto make sufficient progress."
OL,10,FStrikes scheduled for June 16 and 18
OL,11,Fhave also been called off, but the
OL,12,Funion announced new 24-hour strike
OL,13,Fdates of June 2 and 4 if the dispute
OL,14,Fremains unresolved.
OL,16,FThe union says its members oppose a
OL,17,Fnew four day working week arrangement
OL,18,Fon the underground.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@]O]
