OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779199898
OL,3,CTwo 24-hour strikes planned by London
OL,4,CUnderground drivers are called off
OL,6,FNick Dent, director of customer
OL,7,Foperations for London Underground,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are pleased that RMT has
OL,9,Fwithdrawn its planned industrial
OL,10,Faction this week. This is good news
OL,11,Ffor London.
OL,13,F"Our proposal for a voluntary four-day
OL,14,Fweek is designed to improve both work-
OL,15,Flife balance for drivers and the
OL,16,Freliability of service for customers.
OL,17,FWe look forward to further discussions
OL,18,Fon the implementation of these
OL,19,Fproposals with all of our trade
OL,20,Funions."
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU|D@HO]
